                0.087
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "五、选择题"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.055,
                0.094,
                0.202,
                0.109
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(1)【答案】 (C)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.085,
                0.116,
                0.574,
                0.15
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】 \\(\\sum_{n = 1}^{\\infty}(-1)^{n}\\frac{k + n}{n^{2}} = k\\sum_{n = 1}^{\\infty}(-1)^{n}\\frac{1}{n^{2}} +\\sum_{n = 1}^{\\infty}(-1)^{n}\\frac{1}{n},\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.087,
                0.159,
                0.869,
                0.192
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "因为级数 \\(\\sum_{n=1}^{\\infty}(-1)^{n}\\frac{1}{n^{2}}\\) 绝对收敛，级数 \\(\\sum_{n=1}^{\\infty}(-1)^{n}\\frac{1}{n}\\) 条件收敛，所以原级数条件收敛，应选(C)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.055,
                0.199,
                0.202,
                0.214
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(2)【答案】 (D)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.085,
                0.221,
                0.599,
                0.251
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】 \\(I = t\\int_{0}^{\\frac{s}{t}}f(tx)\\mathrm{d}x = \\int_{0}^{\\frac{s}{t}}f(tx)\\mathrm{d}(tx)\\stackrel {tx = u}{=}\\int_{0}^{s}f(u)\\mathrm{d}u,\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.086,
                0.259,
                0.386,
                0.275
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "显然 \\(I\\) 与 \\(s\\) 有关，与 \\(t\\) 无关，应选(D)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.055,
                0.282,
                0.202,
                0.297
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(3)【答案】 (B)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.085,
                0.305,
                0.786,
                0.336
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】由极限的保号性可知，存在 \\(\\delta > 0\\) ，当 \\(0 < |x - a| < \\delta\\) 时，\\(\\frac{f(x) - f(a)}{(x - a)^2} < 0\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.087,
                0.344,
                0.496,
                0.36
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "即 \\(f(x) < f(a)\\)，故 \\(x = a\\) 为极大值点，应选(B)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.055,
                0.368,
                0.202,
                0.383
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "（4）【答案】 (C)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.085,
                0.388,
                0.611,
                0.407
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】由 \\(AA^{*} = |A|E\\) 得出 \\(|\\pmb {A}|\\cdot |\\pmb{A}^{*}| = ||\\pmb {A}|\\pmb {E}| = |\\pmb {A}|^{n}\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.087,
                0.413,
                0.436,
                0.43
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "由 \\(|\\mathbf{A}| = a \\neq 0\\) 得 \\(|\\mathbf{A}^*| = a^{n-1}\\)，应选(C)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.055,
                0.437,
                0.562,
                0.469
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "六、【解】 由 \\(\\lim_{n\\to \\infty}\\left|\\frac{a_{n + 1}}{a_n}\\right| = \\frac{1}{2}\\) ，得幂级数的收敛半径为 \\(R = 2\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.083,
                0.477,
                0.589,
                0.511
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "当 \\(x = -2\\) 时，级数 \\(\\sum_{n=1}^{\\infty} \\frac{1}{n 2^n} (-2)^{n-1} = \\frac{1}{2} \\sum_{n=1}^{\\infty} \\frac{(-1)^{n-1}}{n}\\) 收敛；"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.083,
                0.52,
                0.651,
                0.554
            ],
            "angle": 0,
